title: Allimy Women's High Waisted Straight Ankle Wide Leg Ripped Jeans Frayed Hem Stretchy Capri Denim Pants
description: These wide leg jeans are a 10 out 10! The high waisted jeans has distressed details all over, a high rise and raw hem.
We love that it's complete with five classic pockets and a good amount of stretch for that comfy, wear-all-day feeling.
The high rise wide leg jeans is made of stretch denim fabric . Classical Front zip fly & button closure.
You can choose different wash color and ripped detail .This wide leg jeans is suitable for all seasons. Style it with your favorite spring sweaters and boots or summer shirts.
Machine Wash Cold, Inside Out with Like Colors, Tumble Dry Low
